T*
(timing. Exact time-to-click reuse is selectively calibrated with a 99th-percentile) Tj
T*
(reuse-count cutoff and an absolute floor so the rule can adapt to timer reuse patterns) Tj
T*
(without letting low-count coincidences fire. Confirmed query repetition is intentionally) Tj
