T*
(repeated. Dense burst repetition is also conjunctive: it requires a heavy) Tj
T*
(region/browser/OS cluster, at least five same-second clicks, and a repeated query or) Tj
T*
(query/domain pattern on the same event. The second classifier is an Extended Isolation) Tj
T*
(Forest anomaly model over 15 ML features selected from 15 engineered behavioral) Tj
T*
(features, including region/browser/OS frequency, global ct country frequency, explicit) Tj
T*
(mechanical features for sub-200ms clicks, local burst density, and query entropy. Query) Tj
T*
(length, query word count, and uncertain URL flags are no longer engineered features.) Tj
T*
(High-volume domain frequency and global country frequency remain available but are down-) Tj
T*
(weighted to 0.50 and 0.50, respectively, in the standardized ML matrix. Repetition and) Tj
T*
(timing features that can dominate standalone EIF tail evidence are also down-weighted to) Tj
T*
(0.50: query/domain repetition, query repetition, log-scaled time-to-click magnitude,) Tj
